@krnjn Digging through `resource_updated` => `update_resource` => `resource.update_with_password` the value of `resource_updated` is effectively the same as whether or not the resource is valid/saved: https://github.com/plataformatec/devise/blob/65700b22bab0746a40358dacb32197280acf2888/lib/devise/models/database_authenticatable.rb#L71

That method just sets a validation error if the current password is not correct mainly.

Not sure if this helps or not.
